&lt;h3 id=&#34;error-trappings&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#error-trappings&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Error trappings!&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure to include appropriate exception handling with try catch blocks for any file being processed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Make use of such runtime exceptions such as FileNotFoundException or other possible exceptions that may occur during the processing of any file(s).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;print-formatting-hints&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#print-formatting-hints&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Print formatting hints&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use various print formatting for printing detailed record information especially to make output look professional and columnar like with the format specifier % symbol followed by a converter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Popular converters to use include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%f&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;float&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%d&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;int&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%s&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;string&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%n&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;newline&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
