          &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;item&#34; title=&#34;優萌初華&#34; style=&#34;--block-color:#9d5b8b;&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://shoka.lostyu.me&#34; class=&#34;image&#34; data-background-image=&#34;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amehime/shoka@d1a6bdad/images/404.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;div class=&#34;info&#34;&gt;
          &lt;a href=&#34;https://shoka.lostyu.me&#34; class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;優萌初華&lt;/a&gt;
